description: Try our easy to follow Crumbed Fish & Oven Baked Chips recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Crumbed Fish & Oven Baked Chips Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Bake for 8-10 minutes on top shelf of oven or until golden and fish is cooked. Garnish with chopped parsley and serve with chips, tartare sauce and lemon wedges.
